channel.title: The Hit List
channel.desc: In a star-studded episode, some famous faces are put through their musical paces in this family special! Joining Rochelle and Marvin Humes in this addictively play-along music quiz are actor Kola Bokinni and his sister DJ Yinka Bokinni, Outnumbered stars and on-screen siblings Tyger Drew-Honey and Ramona Marquez, and presenter Stacey Dooley and her partner, dancer Kevin Clifton. Who will get the chance to win ?10,000 for their chosen charity?
